<h2 id="section-top">Rehabilitation care services</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=2807">Cheshire and Wirral Partnership NHS Foundation Trust</a>
</p>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent536bdb29a9214ad789e43ad599925fd9">
</div>
<p><a href="http://www.cwp.nhs.uk/services/389-cardiac-rehabilitation">Cardiac Rehabilitation</a></p>
<p> </p>
<p><img alt="Cardiac Rehabilitation" height="285" src="http://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/platform-cwp-live/images/770/medium.jpg?1380710942"/></p>
<p class="caption">Cardiac Rehabilitation</p>
<p>West Physical Health Services, part of CWP, provide a multidisciplinary service for those who have suffered a heart attack or undergone cardiac surgery (including those with a new diagnosis of heart failure).</p>
<p>This service provides initial clinical assessments and a long-term programme of care which includes exercise, education, symptom control and lifestyle advice.</p>
<p>There are a number of different 'phases' of cardiac rehabilitation care. The Cardiac Rehabilitation team is staffed by specialists/nurses, physiotherapists and exercise physiologists.</p>
<p><strong>Contact</strong></p>
<p>Departmental Manager: Sophie McIntosh, Cardiac Rehabilitation Specialist</p>
<p>Cardiac Rehabilitation Department, The Long House, Countess of Chester Hospital, Liverpool Road, Chester, CH2 1UL</p>
<p>Telephone: 01244 365662, Fax: 01244 365199</p>
<p>Email: <strong><a href="mailto:sophie.mcintosh@nhs.net">sophie.mcintosh@nhs.net</a></strong></p>
<p> </p></div>
